# Agent skills (Callstack)

This repository uses the [agentskills.io](https://agentskills.io/specification) layout. Read the relevant **`SKILL.md` first**, then follow links into `references/`.

## Skill entry points

Use the copy under `skills/` when this repository is checked out; otherwise use the web view:

- [react-native-best-practices](https://github.com/callstackincubator/agent-skills/blob/main/skills/react-native-best-practices/SKILL.md) — RN performance (FPS, lists, native, bundle)
- [github](https://github.com/callstackincubator/agent-skills/blob/main/skills/github/SKILL.md) — PRs, review, branching
- [github-actions](https://github.com/callstackincubator/agent-skills/blob/main/skills/github-actions/SKILL.md) — Actions, simulators, artifacts
- [upgrading-react-native](https://github.com/callstackincubator/agent-skills/blob/main/skills/upgrading-react-native/SKILL.md) — RN / Expo upgrades
- [react-native-brownfield-migration](https://github.com/callstackincubator/agent-skills/blob/main/skills/react-native-brownfield-migration/SKILL.md) — brownfield adoption

## Consuming these rules in another project

If you **imported** this ruleset from GitHub into a different workspace, the markdown files above may not exist locally. Clone or copy the `skills/` tree (see the repository README **Cursor** section) so paths resolve, or ask the user to add the skill files.

## Workflow

Follow **measure → optimize → re-measure**. Prefer profiler evidence over speculative optimizations.
